→ Hello, Carlos! (called 0 times)

> Ask the agent: "Use the hello_lab tool to greet Alice formally"
→ (Agent calls hello_lab tool with {name: "Alice", style: "formal"})
→ Dear Alice

> /hello-lab

→ Hello, world! (called 1 times)
